comments: House Jr. (UTA) and Ayton (PHX) engage and disengage during the off-ball screen and the contact is marginal.
Gobert (UTA) places a forearm to the lower body of Ayton (PHX), and the shot is unaffected by the marginal contact.
Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Crowder (PHX) and brings his arms up to his chest while bracing for contact with the latter.
Ayton (PHX) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Conley (UTA) and the contact is marginal.
Paul (PHX) places and removes his hands from the back of Gobert (UTA) during the rebound and the latter's reaction is not commensurate with the degree of contact.
Bridges (PHX) is established in bounds upon receiving the pass.
House Jr. (UTA) rises to contest the dunk attempt from Bridges (PHX) and there is no contact to the offensive player during the contest.
Booker (PHX) brings his right arm to Conley's (UTA) side as the two players engage and the contact affects his FOM.

Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a wide screening position in the path of Booker (PHX) and the former briefly brushes Booker's left side with his arm. The marginal touch does not inhibit Booker's defensive play.
Conley (UTA) reaches around and makes contact with Bridges' (PHX) left arm after the gather that affects the driving shot attempt at the basket.
Ayton (PHX) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Crowder (PHX) quickly places and removes his left hand from the lower back of Conley (UTA) and the marginal touch does not alter the latter's driving shot attempt.
Booker (PHX) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of Gobert (UTA) and leans forward slightly as he braces for the ensuing marginal contact.
Gobert (UTA) brings his right arm to the body of Ayton (PHX) and slides it off during the layup attempt at the rim and the contact is marginal.
Bogdanovic (UTA) commits a take foul on Paul (PHX).
Paul (PHX) makes contact with Gobert's (UTA) left arm that affects his shot near the rim.
